Blaine Boudreaux has been charged with intoxication manslaughter and intoxicated assault in connection to three separate DUI crashes in Houston . 
  Police say he ran a red light and killed 6-year-old Joshua Medrano and injured his mother Cynthia Medrano on Sunday evening . 
  The suspect also allegedly struck and killed homeless man Leonard Batiste hours earlier . 
  Boud reaux has a history of DUIs in his native Louisiana . 
  He is also accused of crashing into another car carrying a woman and a toddler . 
 